This is the Change Log for the Deacon push notifications library.

=== Version 0.1.1_alpha ===

Corrects the following defects:

* Adds bounds-checking on passed parameters
* Attempts to eliminate leaked BroadcastReceiver object when used in Android

=== Version 0.1.0_alpha ===

This is the initial public release of the Deacon library.

* Basic push notification capability; subscribe, receive, unsubscribe
* Connect to a single Meteor server, create multiple subscriptions
* Basic network connectivity awareness when used in Android
* Delivery of push notifications, errors and connectivity status updates via context callbacks